too hard.

03:07.210 --> 03:09.201
LA. is a tricky place.

03:09.210 --> 03:11.110
L.A.?
It's a movie. [ Chuckles ]

03:11.120 --> 03:12.826
Where do you think they --
they film these things?

03:12.830 --> 03:15.162
[ Chuckles ]
Mm.

03:15.170 --> 03:17.070
You're hesitant.
Yeah, I just --

03:17.080 --> 03:19.662
