and go to Los Angeles.

03:19.670 --> 03:21.456
I'm sure it would only be
a few days.

03:21.460 --> 03:23.166
I-I just --
I can't do that...

03:23.170 --> 03:24.706
right now.

03:24.710 --> 03:26.871
LA. is, um...

03:26.880 --> 03:28.450
It's complicated.

03:28.460 --> 03:30.109
So...

03:30.120 --> 03:32.202
Miss Parios...

03:33.250 --> 03:35.491
...I'm a nobody.

03:35.500 --> 03:36.956
No kids.

03:36.960 --> 03:38.825
