Okay.

04:09.000 --> 04:11.491
Did you say L.A.?
This is a sign!

04:11.500 --> 04:13.161
What is?
This is.

04:13.170 --> 04:15.616
The 1973 Dodge Challenger,
Rallye series.

04:15.620 --> 04:16.951
