it must feel amazing.

11:35.920 --> 11:37.069
Oh, oh.

11:37.080 --> 11:38.911
Truly, I mean, just
something to aspire to.

11:38.920 --> 11:41.115
For me, as --
as a beginner, I --

11:41.120 --> 11:43.247
